column1: I've been flying for quite some time, already.
It seems like I've been flying around in circles from the start.
Who's the one that's been emitting all this strange light this whole time?
This is the mirror world.
You have fallen right into my trap.
This has to be a joke, right? How could this happen?
Why didn't I realize it at all?
You don't know?
It's because of the meteor fragments.
The light radiated by them has made you lose your way.
Actually, these are the things that I used to enhance my magic power.
You've been collecting too much for a human to take.
That is why I am able to trap you easily.
Ah……
I didn't know that these meteor fragments are such troublesome things.
I guess I gotta be more careful next time!
There won't be a next time.
Just wait here obediently until the end of the prayer ritual.
Are you sure about that?
I can leave as long as I beat you right?
That is correct
but can you do it?
There is nothing that firepower cannot solve!
What an arrogant witch!
Since you are so eager to die,
I shall send you off right away!
